== Personal life ==
Rosick<U+00FD> is the son of former league footballer [[Ji<U+0159><U+00ED> Rosick<U+00FD> (footballer born 1948)|Ji<U+0159><U+00ED> Rosick<U+00FD>]], who played as a defender in a career spanning 15 years.<ref name=jerabek/> Tom<U+00E1><U+0161>' son, also named Tom<U+00E1><U+0161>, was born to girlfriend Radka Kocurov<U+00E1> in June 2013.<ref>{{cite news |url=http://revue.idnes.cz/tomas-rosicky-a-radka-kocurova-maji-syna-fdr-/lidicky.aspx?c=A130628_122359_lidicky_nh|title=Tom<U+00E1><U+0161> Rosick<U+00FD> je otcem, Radka Kocurov<U+00E1> porodila syna|language=Czech|trans_title=Tom<U+00E1><U+0161> Rosick<U+00FD> is a father, Radka Kocurov<U+00E1> gave birth to a son|work=idnes.cz|publisher=Mlad<U+00E1> fronta DNES|location=Czech Republic|date=28 June 2013|accessdate=15 June 2014}}</ref> He married Kocurova in May 2014 after having been in a relationship with her for 11 years.<ref>{{cite news |url=http://revue.idnes.cz/tomas-rosicky-a-radka-kocurova-svatba-d82-/sex.aspx?c=A140611_082031_sex_zar|title=Tom<U+00E1><U+0161> Rosick<U+00FD> a Radka Kocurov<U+00E1> se po 11 letech vzali|language=Czech|trans_title=Tom<U+00E1><U+0161> Rosick<U+00FD> and Radka Kocurov<U+00E1> got married after 11 years|work=idnes.cz|publisher=Mlad<U+00E1> fronta DNES|location=Czech Republic|date=11 June 2014|accessdate=15 June 2014}}</ref> He played guitar during a live performance with rock band [[T<U+0159>i sestry]], having practiced his guitar skills during his 18 months on the sidelines because of his hamstring injury.<ref name=guitarhero>{{cite news|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-1254842/Arsenal-maestro-Tomas-Rosicky-turns-guitar-hero-serenade-Chelsea-keeper-Petr-Cech-Czech-Player-Year-awards.html |title= Rock on, Tommy! Arsenal maestro Tomas Rosicky turns guitar hero to serenade Chelsea keeper Petr Cech  |work=Daily Mail |location=London |date= 2 March 2010  |accessdate=12 March 2010 }}</ref>

